T02TD1674E:200a-1: shr'i badzra he ru ka s'adha na n'a ma /
T02TD1674E:200b-0: dpal he ru ka'i sgrub pa'i thabs zhes @200b bya ba ;
T02TD1674E:200b-1: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1674E:200b-2: mgon po bde chen las byung ba'i //
T02TD1674E:200b-3: rigs sku ye shes kun gyi bdag / dregs byed rgyu 'bras 'joms mdzad pa'i //
T02TD1674E:200b-4: stobs chen khro rgyal dpal la 'dud //
T02TD1674E:200b-5: yang dag grub pa'i las gzhung gi //
T02TD1674E:200b-6: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yi rim ba las /
T02TD1674E:200b-7: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD1674E:200b-8: dgos don 'brel pa'i sgo nas bshad //
T02TD1674E:200b-9: rtsod dus sems can gdul dka' zhing //
T02TD1674E:200b-10: log pa'i lam la gnas dag la //
T02TD1674E:200b-11: mdzad spyod zhi bas mi 'dul phyir //
T02TD1674E:200b-12: khro bo'i phrin las bstan pa yin //
T02TD1674E:200b-13: de nyid grub pa'i gzhung dag la //
T02TD1674E:200b-14: log rtog 'khrul pas bslad pa dag / nges pa'i gzhung don rtogs bya'i phyir //
T02TD1674E:200b-15: legs bsdus bstan pa gsal bar bya //
T02TD1674E:200b-17: shes rab kyis ni blo phye nas //
T02TD1674E:200b-18: nges par brtag pa'i sa gzhi las//
T02TD1674E:200b-19: bla mas nges pa'i lung 'di bstan //
T02TD1674E:200b-20: snum pa yi ni dam tshig dang //
T02TD1674E:200b-21: gtsang dang 'jigs pa'i brtul zhugs can //
T02TD1674E:200b-22: de dag goms nas nyams su blang //
T02TD1674E:200b-23: grub pa'i dpang phyug phung sum tshogs //
T02TD1674E:200b-24: blo zhan shes rab chung bas ni //
T02TD1674E:200b-25: bsgrubs kyang grub par mi 'gyur te /
T02TD1674E:200b-26: phung byed gnyi ga bsregs pas na //
T02TD1674E:200b-27: de bas gzhan du bstan pa mi //
T02TD1674E:200b-28: dur khrod dang ni lha rten dang /
T02TD1674E:200b-29: ma mo'i gnas la sogs 'dug nas //
T02TD1674E:200b-30: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dgos pa dag / rnam pa du mar 'grub par 'gyur //
T02TD1674E:200b-31: phyi dang nang gi rdzas bsags nas //
T02TD1674E:200b-32: rang rgyud dag pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1674E:200b-33: bgegs tshogs nye bar zhi bya dang //
T02TD1674E:200b-34: tshogs bsags bsrung ba'i don ched du //
T02TD1674E:200b-35: 'byung po'i gtor ma btang nas ni //
T02TD1674E:200b-36: gsang ba'i don gyi las rnams bya //
T02TD1674E:200b-37: bdag nyid rang gi lhar sbyor bas //
T02TD1674E:200b-38: lus ngag yid gsum mthu bskyed cing //
T02TD1674E:200b-39: bdag dang 'gro ba spyang byas nas //
T02TD1674E:200b-40: rang bzhin dag pa'i rnam par bsam //
T02TD1674E:200b-42: dkyil 'khor mdun du bsam byas nas //
T02TD1674E:200b-43: rtse gcig sems kyis mchod sogs dang //
T02TD1674E:200b-44: 'gro don spyod pa rgya cher bya //
T02TD1674E:200b-45: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa //
T02TD1674E:201a-1: rje che dang ldan pa yi //
T02TD1674E:201a-2: dkyil 'khor lnga la sogs pa yi //
T02TD1674E:201a-3: zhi ba'i mchod pas mnyes byas te //
T02TD1674E:201a-4: bsnyen pa'i dus su goms byas nas //
T02TD1674E:201a-5: 'khor bcas mchod ba rdzogs par bya //
T02TD1674E:201a-6: de yang spyi dang so so yi //
T02TD1674E:201a-7: sgrub pa'i bye brag rnam gnyis te //
T02TD1674E:201a-8: bsdus dang rgyas la dga' ba yi //
T02TD1674E:201a-9: dbye ba gnyis su shes par bya //
T02TD1674E:201a-10: dang por chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
T02TD1674E:201a-11: dmigs pa med pa'i don gyis bsgom //
T02TD1674E:201a-12: dngos po med par bdag sbyor bas //
T02TD1674E:201a-13: nam mkha' kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'o //
T02TD1674E:201a-14: aom ma h'a sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1674E:201a-15: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
T02TD1674E:201a-16: thams cad du ni khyab pa las //
T02TD1674E:201a-17: chos kun stong gsal rang bzhin med //
T02TD1674E:201a-18: mi dmigs snying rje chen po'i dang //
T02TD1674E:201a-19: aom dharma th'a tu sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1674E:201a-20: skad cig ma yis skur gnas te //
T02TD1674E:201a-22: rdo rje rgya gram sa gzhi la //
T02TD1674E:201a-23: ra ba gur dang bla re dang //
T02TD1674E:201a-25: mtshon cha'i phreng bas 'khor bar bsgom //
T02TD1674E:201a-26: rdo rje sems dpa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD1674E:201a-27: mkha' dbyings sna tshogs la gnas nas //
T02TD1674E:201a-28: cir yang gyur pa'i yig 'bru las //
T02TD1674E:201a-29: 'od zer tshul du spros nas kyang //
T02TD1674E:201a-30: ma lus nye bar khyab byas te //
T02TD1674E:201a-31: re zhig rngam pa'i tshul du dgongs //
T02TD1674E:201a-32: ae las mkha' dbyings gru gsum dkar //
T02TD1674E:201a-33: bzang po'i mkha' dbyings gyen bsgreng nas //
T02TD1674E:201a-34: yam las rlung dkyil gzhu yi dbyibs //
T02TD1674E:201a-35: dud kha sra mkhregs sgrol ma'i mkha' //
T02TD1674E:201a-36: ram las me 'od dmar ser las //
T02TD1674E:201a-37: gru gsum gos dkar nam mkha'i dbyings //
T02TD1674E:201a-38: bam las chu dkyil dkar zhing zlum //
T02TD1674E:201a-39: bum pas mtshan pa m'a ma k'i //
T02TD1674E:201a-40: lam las gser gyi sa gzhi ste //
T02TD1674E:201a-41: gru bzhi spyan la rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1674E:201a-43: 'dod chags chen po'i rang bzhin rtags //
T02TD1674E:201a-44: kam byung ker rus ri rab ste //
T02TD1674E:201a-45: rin chen rgyan spras rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1674E:201a-46: de dbus bh'um las gzhal yas khang //
T02TD1674E:201a-47: gru bzhi sgo dang sgo khyud can //
T02TD1674E:201a-48: rin chen thong pa sna tshogs dang //
T02TD1674E:201a-49: nyi zla rdo rje'i rgyan gyis mdzes //
T02TD1674E:201a-50: dkyil 'khor zla gam gnas pa la //
T02TD1674E:201a-51: re'u mig dgu pa rdo rjes mdzes //
T02TD1674E:201b-0: sna tshogs lha mo'i @201b phreng ba dang //
T02TD1674E:201b-1: 'phan gdugs rnga yab rta babs ldan //
T02TD1674E:201b-2: zhing 'phrul tshangs pa'i g-yang gzhi sogs //
T02TD1674E:201b-3: dur khrod rgyan gyis 'jigs par brgyan //
T02TD1674E:201b-4: rin chen ka gdung tog dang bcas //
T02TD1674E:201b-5: 'dod yon sna tshogs rgyan gyis mdzes //
T02TD1674E:201b-6: dkyil 'khor phyi ri ma gnas brgyad du //
T02TD1674E:201b-7: dur khrod shing dang zhing skyod dang //
T02TD1674E:201b-8: phyogs skyong rnal 'byor mtsho dang sprin //
T02TD1674E:201b-9: klu rgyal la sogs gnas brgyad du //
T02TD1674E:201b-10: sha za 'byung po gshin rje dang //
T02TD1674E:201b-11: mkha' 'gro bya kyi ro la sogs //
T02TD1674E:201b-12: ce spyad khro tshogs sgra'i 'byin cing //
T02TD1674E:201b-13: ro yi tshogs la longs spyod mdzad //
T02TD1674E:201b-14: rang byung mchod rten dang bcas pa //
T02TD1674E:201b-15: phreng ba rim gsum phyi rol gnas //
T02TD1674E:201b-16: de dbus 'khor lo'i lta ba la //
T02TD1674E:201b-17: padma dregs byed nyi zla'i steng //
T02TD1674E:201b-18: dpal mchog dang po gnas gyur nas //
T02TD1674E:201b-19: sprul pa'i ting 'dzin la gnas mdzad //
T02TD1674E:201b-20: chos rnams thams cad rnam brtags na //
T02TD1674E:201b-21: dngos med mtshan ma kun dang bral //
T02TD1674E:201b-22: byang sems ye shes dang po'i gzugs //
T02TD1674E:201b-23: a'a li zla dkyil gsal bar bsgom //
T02TD1674E:201b-24: byang sems ye shes gnyis pa'i rtags //
T02TD1674E:201b-25: de steng k'a li nyi mar bcas //
T02TD1674E:201b-26: mtshan dang dpe byad gsal ba'i don //
T02TD1674E:201b-28: de dag 'od du gyur pa las //
T02TD1674E:201b-29: h'um las rdo rje rtse lnga pa ;
T02TD1674E:201b-30: / dkar po bum pa h'um gis mtshan //
T02TD1674E:201b-32: gdod ma tha ma med pa'i dbyings //
T02TD1674E:201b-33: dang po rdo rje chen po yin //
T02TD1674E:201b-35: dkyil 'khor drug gi las mdzad nas //
T02TD1674E:201b-36: sku gsung thugs dbyings bzhugs pa las //
T02TD1674E:201b-37: 'od zer phreng mdzes brjid pa'i mchog / de la sku mchog phyag rgya yi //
T02TD1674E:201b-38: sngags kyi yi ge brjod par bya //
T02TD1674E:201b-39: aom ma h'a su kha badzra sa tva aa /
T02TD1674E:201b-41: de dag ye shes byang chub sems //
T02TD1674E:201b-42: mngon byang lnga yi bdag nyid do //
T02TD1674E:201b-43: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' che //
T02TD1674E:201b-44: dkar dmar zhal lnga phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD1674E:201b-45: rdo rje kha tv'am rdo rjer bcas /'og ma gnyis kyis mda' dang gzhu //
T02TD1674E:201b-46: rin chen rgyan dang na bza' can //
T02TD1674E:201b-47: dbu la rin chen phreng bas mdzes //
T02TD1674E:201b-48: lus kyi ba spu'i gnas rnams su //
T02TD1674E:201b-49: dkyil 'khor drug gi rdul phran gnas //
T02TD1674E:201b-50: rdo rje rtse lnga'i phyag rgya ni //
T02TD1674E:202a-2: sngags kyis bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
T02TD1674E:202a-3: sku gsung thugs sogs rnam par bsam //
T02TD1674E:202a-4: aom na ma: sarba ta th'a ga ta k'a ya w'a ka tsitta gu na karma badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1674E:202a-6: gsang gnas h'um dang a'as brgyan te //
T02TD1674E:202a-7: ye shes rdo rje phata dang bcas //
T02TD1674E:202a-8: rtse mo nor bu 'bar bas mtshan //
T02TD1674E:202a-9: rnam thar padma ae dkyil can //
T02TD1674E:202a-10: mdog ser lte ba ze'u 'bru dmar //
T02TD1674E:202a-11: sa ma ya sogs brdas bskul nas //
T02TD1674E:202a-12: dza: h'um bam ho: sa rol pa bya //
T02TD1674E:202a-13: aom pra be sha ya phata /
T02TD1674E:202a-14: aa la la la la ho //
T02TD1674E:202a-15: bde ba chen po'i 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1674E:202a-16: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba mnyes mdzad nas //
T02TD1674E:202a-17: 'gro ba'i lus ngag yid gsum spyang //
T02TD1674E:202a-18: sku gsung thugs kyi rgyan gyis brjid //
T02TD1674E:202a-19: thams cad 'od kyis slar bsdus nas //
T02TD1674E:202a-21: sangs rgyas drug gi gsung du gyur //
T02TD1674E:202a-22: ba spu'i bu ga kun du thim //
T02TD1674E:202a-23: thugs ka'i gnas su zhugs pa dag / bde ba chen po'i gnas nas babs //
T02TD1674E:202a-24: 'dod chags chen po dga' ba'i mes //
T02TD1674E:202a-25: sku dang bcas pa 'od du gyur //
T02TD1674E:202a-26: sngon gyi goms shugs lha mo bzhis //
T02TD1674E:202a-27: phyogs bzhi nas ni bskul mdzad de //
T02TD1674E:202a-28: stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor yod med mthu //
T02TD1674E:202a-29: nam mkha' nyid du dam tshig nye bar gnas //
T02TD1674E:202a-30: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs pa bzhengs su gsol //
T02TD1674E:202a-31: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag / ye shes gsang ba'i rgyud bskul nas //
T02TD1674E:202a-32: thugs rjes 'gro la gzigs mdzad de//
T02TD1674E:202a-33: 'bras bu'i sems dpa' snga ma bzhin //
T02TD1674E:202a-34: cho ga gsum gyis gsal bar bya //
T02TD1674E:202a-35: de nas bcom ldan rdo rje can //
T02TD1674E:202a-36: rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1674E:202a-37: rdo rje se go la phyag rgyas ni //
T02TD1674E:202a-38: sangs rgyas thams cad bsdu bar mdzad //
T02TD1674E:202a-39: 'jig rten khams ni ma lus pa //
T02TD1674E:202a-40: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin bcas rgyan //
T02TD1674E:202a-41: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
T02TD1674E:202a-42: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
T02TD1674E:202a-43: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo las //
T02TD1674E:202a-44: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
T02TD1674E:202a-45: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
T02TD1674E:202a-46: 'jig rten gsum dag sreg byed na //
T02TD1674E:202b-0: sangs rgyas thams cad @202b khros pa yis //
T02TD1674E:202b-1: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
T02TD1674E:202b-2: de nas sna yi rtse mo la //
T02TD1674E:202b-3: yid ni yang dag brtan par gzung //
T02TD1674E:202b-4: sna yi dbugs ring dro ba las //
T02TD1674E:202b-5: rgyal ba'i sbyor ba'i phyag rgya 'byung //
T02TD1674E:202b-6: bcom ldan de nyid rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1674E:202b-7: rdo rje khro bor bsgyur nas phyung //
T02TD1674E:202b-8: aom shr'i he ru ka sa ma ya he:sarba dushta /
T02TD1674E:202b-9: sa ma ya mu dra pra bham dza ka h'um phat /
T02TD1674E:202b-10: snga ma las ni gnas gyur te //
T02TD1674E:202b-11: bskal pa'i me dpung 'khrigs pa bzhin //
T02TD1674E:202b-14: zhal g-yas zhi ba'i rang bzhin dkar //
T02TD1674E:202b-15: dbus ma mthing na gnag po'i zhal //
T02TD1674E:202b-16: g-yon pa rmongs byed ser po ste //
T02TD1674E:202b-17: rgyab ma chags mdzad dmar po'o //
T02TD1674E:202b-18: smin mtshams khro gnyer glog bzhin 'gyu //
T02TD1674E:202b-19: spyan gsum khro gnyer mche gtsigs zhal //
T02TD1674E:202b-20: dbu skra smar ser nag mdzes //
T02TD1674E:202b-21: spu rnams rdo rje gyen du 'khyil //
T02TD1674E:202b-22: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung //
T02TD1674E:202b-23: dgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par byed //
T02TD1674E:202b-24: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba yi //
T02TD1674E:202b-25: sku gsung thugs kyi gar thabs can //
T02TD1674E:202b-26: g-yas g-yon dang pos rdo rje dang //
T02TD1674E:202b-27: rdo rje khatv'am dril bur bcas //
T02TD1674E:202b-29: pags pa bklubs kyi tshul du bskor//
T02TD1674E:202b-30: gsum pa gnyis na mnga' dang gzhu //
T02TD1674E:202b-31: g-yas kyi bzhi pas dung khrag 'dzin //
T02TD1674E:202b-32: g-yon kyi bzhi pas thod pa ru //
T02TD1674E:202b-33: snying chen po yis bkang pa'o //
T02TD1674E:202b-34: la lar zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
T02TD1674E:202b-36: g-yas pas ba dan gsum pa phyar //
T02TD1674E:202b-37: rdo rje rtse lnga 'bar phreng can //
T02TD1674E:202b-38: rdo rje kha tv'am dril bur bcas //
T02TD1674E:202b-39: thod pa gang ba g-yon pa na //
T02TD1674E:202b-41: thod pa mang po'i dbu rgyan can //
T02TD1674E:202b-42: 'jigs pa chen po'i dus ltar drag / drug khrod bzhin du rab tu 'jigs //
T02TD1674E:202b-43: zhal rnams sna tshogs 'gyur ba dang //
T02TD1674E:202b-44: 'bar ba'i lta bas gar byed pa //
T02TD1674E:202b-45: rdo rje rdo rje kha tv'am ga //
T02TD1674E:202b-46: dril bu'i sgra ni gsil ba yis //
T02TD1674E:202b-47: thams cad phab nas slar yang ni //
T02TD1674E:202b-48: thal bar gyur pa 'ang 'tsho bar byed //
T02TD1674E:202b-49: gti mug dbang mdzad theg chen brgyan //
T02TD1674E:202b-50: glang chen kon rlon stod g-yogs man bas //
T02TD1674E:203a-2: / tshar bcad stag gi pags pa yin //
T02TD1674E:203a-3: nga rgyal thugs rjes 'gro sgrol rtags //
T02TD1674E:203a-5: zhe sdang gzung 'dzin rnam dag pas //
T02TD1674E:203a-6: gnas brgyad sprul gyi phreng ba can //
T02TD1674E:203a-7: chags pa gnyis dang ldan pa yis //
T02TD1674E:203a-8: sku la rakta'i thig les brgyan //
T02TD1674E:203a-9: phrin las sna tshogs mdzad pa yis //
T02TD1674E:203a-10: thal ba'i tshom bus mtshan pa yin //
T02TD1674E:203a-11: byang sems gnyis med dri bral don //
T02TD1674E:203a-12: zhag gi ri mos spras pa'o //
T02TD1674E:203a-13: phrag dog sku gsung rgyan ldan pas //
T02TD1674E:203a-14: thod phreng thod dang se ral thogs //
T02TD1674E:203a-15: dregs byed zil gyis mnan pa'i phyir//
T02TD1674E:203a-16: nyi zla snyan gyi gong rgyan byas //
T02TD1674E:203a-17: lus dang ngag sems rdo rje yi //
T02TD1674E:203a-18: mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar ldan byas te //
T02TD1674E:203a-19: thams cad 'byung ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1674E:203a-20: bdag gi slar ni bdag nyid bya //
T02TD1674E:203a-22: thugs gsal nyi ma la gnas pa'i //
T02TD1674E:203a-23: ye shes sems dpa' hr'i: dang bcas //
T02TD1674E:203a-25: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te //
T02TD1674E:203a-26: lha mos bdud rtsi'i bum pas dkris //
T02TD1674E:203a-27: thod phreng la gnas rigs lngas brgyan //
T02TD1674E:203a-28: lag pa shin tu brkyang pa yis //
T02TD1674E:203a-29: mdzub mo gnyis ni mdud par bcing //
T02TD1674E:203a-30: gung mo mthe bo'i rtse mo can //
T02TD1674E:203a-31: rdo rje'i phyag rgya yongs su bsgyur //
T02TD1674E:203a-32: bteg nas khro gnyer lag bzhag ste //
T02TD1674E:203a-33: hi bcas dbang bskur sngags brjod bya //
T02TD1674E:203a-34: yab yum mkha' gsang hi dang aas //
T02TD1674E:203a-35: rdo rje padmar bskyed byas nas //
T02TD1674E:203a-37: brla yi dbus su bsgom byas nas //
T02TD1674E:203a-40: byang chub sems de kun du dgod //
T02TD1674E:203a-41: ma lus nye bar khyab byas nas //
T02TD1674E:203a-42: 'dod par bya ba rab tu mnyes //
T02TD1674E:203a-44: gsang gnas so so'i gdan dag la //
T02TD1674E:203a-45: chos kyi snying po'i lha gnas bskyed //
T02TD1674E:203a-46: hr'i: las dpal chen he ru ka / gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dbus su dgod //
T02TD1674E:203a-47: hr'i:las lha mo goo r'i ma //
T02TD1674E:203a-48: hni:las de bzhin tsoo r'i ma //
T02TD1674E:203a-49: dzhi: las lha mo pra mo yin //
T02TD1674E:203a-50: dzhi las betta phyogs bzhir dgod //
T02TD1674E:203a-51: mtshams su h'um phat las byung ba'i //
T02TD1674E:203a-52: lha mo pukka la sogs bzhi //
T02TD1674E:203a-53: mam kham yam ram las byung ba'i //

T02TD1674E:206b-35: bza' ba la sogs snying po can //
T02TD1674E:206b-36: mam sa la sogs bro mchog stsol //
T02TD1674E:206b-37: me tog la sogs tsandan phreng //
T02TD1674E:206b-38: bzang dgur dbul lo bzhes su gsol //
T02TD1674E:206b-39: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog / byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD1674E:206b-40: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
T02TD1674E:206b-41: h'um dang phat kyis ldan par brjod //
T02TD1674E:206b-42: aom shin tu brgyan pa'i rigs dang mtshan ldan mchog / bkra shis dbyangs dang gar gyis bskyod pa yis //
T02TD1674E:206b-43: lha mo rdul snyed phyogs bcur spro byas nas //
T02TD1674E:206b-44: byang sems bde ba'i mchod pa'i rnam par rol //
T02TD1674E:206b-46: ma h'a su kha bodhi tsitta aa la la la la ho //
T02TD1674E:206b-47: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
T02TD1674E:206b-48: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
T02TD1674E:206b-49: dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te //
T02TD1674E:206b-50: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
T02TD1674E:206b-51: zhing chen gsar snying sti rar bcas //
T02TD1674E:206b-52: dmar byi aa rgha rgya mtsho bskyil //
T02TD1674E:206b-54: ma lus bzhes nas bsnams su gsol //
T02TD1674E:206b-62: hri daya pi pa h'um phat /
T02TD1674E:206b-63: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
T02TD1674E:206b-64: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
T02TD1674E:207a-2: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
T02TD1674E:207a-4: shr'i he ru ka ma h'a badzra sa ma ya /
T02TD1674E:207a-9: ma h'a panytsa ai mra ta /
T02TD1674E:207a-10: ma h'a aa rgham pra t'i tstsha ho //
T02TD1674E:207a-13: h'um bhyo h'um bhyo h'um bhyo //
T02TD1674E:207a-24: rnam dag sgrib spyang srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
T02TD1674E:207a-25: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
T02TD1674E:207a-26: bcom ldan bde gshegs dri med rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor dbyings //
T02TD1674E:207a-27: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i yab ;
T02TD1674E:207a-28: / shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
T02TD1674E:207a-29: phyag rgya gtum chen rngam pa'i tshogs la sogs //
T02TD1674E:207a-30: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rnams rdzogs //
T02TD1674E:207a-31: dgyes shing rol pa'i dus mchod sbyar ba 'di //
T02TD1674E:207a-32: bzhes te aa la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
T02TD1674E:207a-35: sa ma ya bag sha h'u /
T02TD1674E:207a-36: ru lu ru lu h'um bhyo h'u /
T02TD1674E:207a-39: pra ti dza: h'um bam ho:/
T02TD1674E:207a-40: ya nas mnyam nyid chos sku dag pa las //
T02TD1674E:207a-41: log rtog dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
T02TD1674E:207a-42: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
T02TD1674E:207a-43: de bzlog don du rgyal ba'i dam mnos pas //
T02TD1674E:207a-44: rgyal ba zhi khro'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
T02TD1674E:207a-45: thugs rje'i dang can rnams la bzod par gsol //
T02TD1674E:207a-46: bcom ldan rdo rje dpal chen he ru ka / khyod kyi thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
T02TD1674E:207a-47: mkha' 'gro'i dkyil 'khor tshogs dang bcas pa yis //
T02TD1674E:207a-48: 'grol brtser dgongs tshangs par stsal du gsol //
T02TD1674E:207a-49: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du zhugs pa rnams //
T02TD1674E:207a-50: bcad gtubs lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur zhing //
T02TD1674E:207a-51: grib mas phog pa'i sdug bsngal mi bzod pa //
T02TD1674E:207a-52: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
T02TD1674E:207a-53: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa bye ba stong phrag gi /'od kyis phog pas 'jig rten khams su snang ba dang //
T02TD1674E:207a-54: lus ngag sems dang tshe ni rdo rje rab gnas te //
T02TD1674E:207a-55: re smon thams cad dus 'dir grub par mdzad du gsol //
T02TD1674E:207a-56: ye shes sems dpa'i sngags 'khor lo //
T02TD1674E:207a-57: lha rnams kun gyi gnas zhugs pa //
T02TD1674E:207b-0: yan @207b lag rnam gsum ldan byas te //
T02TD1674E:207b-1: gsal ba gnyis kyi sgo nas brtsam //
T02TD1674E:207b-2: dang po rten dang brten pa'i sngags //
T02TD1674E:207b-3: 'khor lo'i tshul ldan shes rab thabs //
T02TD1674E:207b-4: yi ge mtshan ma sku yi gnas //
T02TD1674E:207b-5: bgrang dang bgrang ba las 'das pa'o //
T02TD1674E:207b-6: rtse gcig gnas su 'khor ba dang //
T02TD1674E:207b-7: langs dang rgyu dang 'phro ba las //
T02TD1674E:207b-8: mchod bskul las mdzad bsdu byed cing //
T02TD1674E:207b-10: las kyi sbyor ba kun sbyor zhing //
T02TD1674E:207b-11: dbyangs drug blangs pas don drug gsal //
T02TD1674E:207b-12: aom ru lu ru lu h'um bhyo h'um /
T02TD1674E:207b-13: thun mong gi snying po phrin las kun la 'jug pa'i yi ge 'bru brgyad pa'o //
T02TD1674E:207b-14: so so'i las la snyoms 'jug nas //
T02TD1674E:207b-15: rang gi mtshan ma sngags dang bcas //
T02TD1674E:207b-17: sku gsung thugs ldan bzlas par bya //
T02TD1674E:207b-18: aom shr'i he ru ka badzra sa ma ya hi /
T02TD1674E:207b-19: sarba dusht'a na sa ya mu dra pra bam dza ka h'um phat /
T02TD1674E:207b-20: khyad par gyi snying po rtsa ba'i sngags yi ge nyi shu rtsa drug pa'o //
T02TD1674E:207b-21: sngags gzhan rim bzhin gsal ldan pas //
T02TD1674E:207b-22: go rims 'khrul med bzlas brjod bya //
T02TD1674E:207b-23: las rdzogs mchod bstod bskul bya zhing //
T02TD1674E:207b-24: rang gi gnas su bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1674E:207b-25: mnyam nyid dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog / don dam bde ba chen po'i sku //
T02TD1674E:207b-26: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes sku //
T02TD1674E:207b-27: lha nyid brtson pas bsgom par bya //
T02TD1674E:207b-28: gzhan yang thig le 'am phra mo dag / lha dang dkyil 'khor rnam dag gi //
T02TD1674E:207b-29: mtshan mas dmigs pa spyang byas te //
T02TD1674E:207b-30: chos sku'i phyag rgya chen por gnas //
T02TD1674E:207b-31: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal byas nas //
T02TD1674E:207b-32: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pas grub byed pa'i //
T02TD1674E:207b-33: tshogs kyi dga' bde'i longs spyod kyis //
T02TD1674E:207b-34: rnal 'byor tshogs kun mnyes byas so //
T02TD1674E:207b-35: rta mchog mkha' 'gro'i tshogs bcas ba //
T02TD1674E:207b-36: lhag ma'i mchod pas mnyes byas nas //
T02TD1674E:207b-37: rang gi las la sbyar byas te //
T02TD1674E:207b-38: dngos grub don phyir mtshams su gzhag / gang zhig thun bzhi la sogs par //
T02TD1674E:207b-39: dkyil 'khor de nyid bsgoms pas ni //
T02TD1674E:207b-40: ye shes dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1674E:207b-41: dam tshig dkyil 'khor rim bzhin bsdu //
T02TD1674E:207b-42: slar nyid sbyor ldan bsrung byas te //
T02TD1674E:208a-2: / tshogs 'gyur spyod lam bya ba yis //
T02TD1674E:208a-3: dus kun du ni 'gro don brtsam //
T02TD1674E:208a-4: sa stengs 'gro la grags pa yis //
T02TD1674E:208a-5: 'gro la thugs rje rnam dag ston //
T02TD1674E:208a-7: bde ba'i grol lam stong gsal mdzad //
T02TD1674E:208a-8: srin bus grong khyer gsal min yang //
T02TD1674E:208a-9: dman rnams don phyir cung zad zhig / sgrub don dam pa'i gzhung gsal byas //
T02TD1674E:208a-10: grags sogs ngan rtog blos ma yin //
T02TD1674E:208a-11: thugs rje'i dgongs mdzad ji lta bzhin //
T02TD1674E:208a-12: ngal ba las byung nyi zer gyis //
T02TD1674E:208a-13: khams gsum mun sogs sel mdzad nas //
T02TD1674E:208a-14: yang dag grub pa'i 'bras thob shog / dpal he ru ka'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD1674E:208a-15: slob dpon chen po h'um mdzad rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1674E:208a-17: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po bidya ka ra sidha dang /
T02TD1674E:208a-18: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba bande lha rin po ches bsgyur cing gtan la phab pa'o /
